{"type": "article", "id": 3712, "title": "Nick Wooster & Birchbox联名收纳包袋", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-20T07:43:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052332131XxoLy5iOHlna6mD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tNick Wooster 曾被时尚媒体誉为「全世界最会穿衣服的男人」。日前，美国纽约的电子商务网站 Birchbox 就邀请这位时尚偶像为网站旗下的 Birchbox Man 设计了一系列联名收纳包袋，以方便用户更高效地收纳出行物品。这一系列产品分为 4 款不同功能的包袋，采用深蓝色羊毛物料制作而成，搭配以橙色与白色的条纹元素，其中既有收纳头戴式耳机与 iPad mini 的「Headphone Flight Bag」，收纳各类充电设备与杂物的「Driving Bag」，亦有可以容纳两幅眼镜的「Sunglasses Bag」和收纳个人护理用品的「Dopp Kit」。定价 38－50 美元不等，<a href=\"https://www.birchbox.com/men/brands/wooster\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe src=\"http://www.tudou.com/programs/view/html5embed.action?type=0&amp;code=cJsqZD-l9Ig&amp;lcode=&amp;resourceId=0_06_05_99\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"width:640px;height:400px;\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233209fG2N70XnkixuYp3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233209yGbZTXN3B8anD0lk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233210srlxTRFI2nZAPtgM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233210PqOy1XSGhkf3JgnZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233211epIkuchRZ7X9LPVm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}